## 6. MCP Taxonomy ‚Äî **This Is the Core of Your Question**

You asked:

> ‚ÄúHow many MCP (Cell / Cluster / Domain) should I categorise?‚Äù

### **Answer: Three Layers. Exactly.**

No more. No less.

